office on the Energy Team.

00:01:00.050 --> 00:01:00.870
A really great guy.

00:01:00.870 --> 00:01:03.060
I'm just so happy that he
connected me with Candice.

00:01:03.060 --> 00:01:05.030
And I've enjoyed
getting to know her

00:01:05.030 --> 00:01:06.890
