00:17:16.319 --> 00:17:17.420
orchestra.

00:17:17.420 --> 00:17:21.430
And he's an amazing collaborator
who came onto this project

00:17:21.430 --> 00:17:24.160
and arranged music
for the album.

00:17:24.160 --> 00:17:29.840
And this is our very
special, special musician,

00:17:29.840 --> 00:17:31.664
Vincent Gardner on trombone.

00:17:31.664 --> 00:17:34.700
